             was indicted for <rs id="t17720603-45-off211" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17720603-45-off211" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720603-45-off211" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously forging a certain order for the payment of money
            </rs>, as follows, No. 1112 Cornhill, Lond. March 12, 1772.</p>
               <p>Mess. Raymond, Williams, Vere, Lowe and Fletcher.</p>
               <p>Pay to Mr. 
               <persName id="t17720603-45-person494">
                  Wm.
                   Clark
               <interp inst="t17720603-45-person494" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
