                  </persName>
            , or bearer, fifteen pounds fifteen shillings.</p>
               <p>Rt. Vennist and Co.</p>
               <p>with intention to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t17720603-45-victim496" type="victimName">
                     John
                      Clarke
                  <interp inst="t17720603-45-victim496" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
